		<li>Axis_placement_3d - moved to <express_ref linkend="Elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm"/>.</li>
	</ul>

<p>The following ARM EXPRESS declarations and interface specifications have been modified:</p>
